-1.plot: Andrea Merriman was living the American Dream: four beautiful children, a gorgeous home and a husband who had a knack for making money. But after 20 years of marriage, Andrea would see that behind her husband's business sense...was an explosive secret!

imdb.title: Who the (Bleep) Did I Marry
plot: A biography about real people who marry their "soulmates", until they learn that the person they thought they married, isn't who they say they are.::Andi Langston
